      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "这些信号是如何被处理、传输和存储的？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
