      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22464,
      "text": "信号处理正是研究这些问题的学科。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.3,
      "size": 20736,
      "text": "信号可以在时域或频域中分析。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "时域显示信号随时间的变化，频域显示信号包含的频率成分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "傅里叶变换是连接时域和频域的桥梁。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.23,
      "size": 19728,
      "text": "让我们通过实例来理解这些概念。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "sampling",
      "line_id": "samp-1",
      "filename": "sampling-samp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/sampling-samp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.33,
      "size": 21312,
      "text": "数字信号是对连续信号的采样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "sampling",
      "line_id": "samp-2",
      "filename": "sampling-samp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/sampling-samp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "采样定理告诉我们：采样频率必须大于信号最高频率的两倍。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "sampling",
      "line_id": "samp-3",
      "filename": "sampling-samp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/sampling-samp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "否则会产生混叠，无法正确恢复原信号。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "sampling",
      "line_id": "samp-4",
      "filename": "sampling-samp-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/sampling-samp-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.99,
      "size": 47808,
      "text": "这就是为什么CD的采样率是44.1kHz，因为人耳能听到的最高频率约20kHz。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "filter",
      "line_id": "filt-1",
      "filename": "filter-filt-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/filter-filt-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "滤波器用于选择性地保留或去除某些频率成分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "filter",
      "line_id": "filt-2",
      "filename": "filter-filt-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/filter-filt-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "低通滤波器保留低频，去除高频，用于去噪。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "filter",
      "line_id": "filt-3",
      "filename": "filter-filt-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/filter-filt-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "高通滤波器保留高频，去除低频，用于边缘检测。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "filter",
      "line_id": "filt-4",
      "filename": "filter-filt-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/filter-filt-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "带通滤波器只保留特定频率范围，用于信号分离。"
    },
    {
